# Product Scope Rule

## Intent
Focus on building a lean, hybrid data MVP that serves Victorian drivers by combining official delayed data with real-time community reports.

## Guidelines
- Avoid heavy infrastructure (e.g. Kafka, background workers) unless user traffic and scale explicitly demand it.
- Opt for direct-to-database writes for community reports.
- Emphasize hyper-local, actionable features (e.g. route optimization, hourly suburb trends).
- Ensure the app provides high value with minimal operational overhead.